patchlogs.name: Update 30.7: Nidus Prime & Plague Star
patchlogs.changes:
For a long time now we’ve had a precedent with a handful of Warframe Skins where the “None” option for Attachments (and sometimes Syandanas) was removed if certain Skins, Primes, etc were equipped. This applied to Warframes such as Ember Prime/Pyraxis Skin, Frost, Mag Prime, Oberon, Volt, etc.
We now usher in a new “None” era! All Warframes and Warframe Skins that previously did not have the ‘None’ option will have a “None” Attachment or Syandana option, giving you even MORE customization flexibility. This means you can remove details such as any attachments on Ember Pyraxis, Mag Prime, the list goes on and on! In addition, Banshee, Frost and Oberon's default Shoulder Armor can now be equipped on Prime versions of the Warframe.

Railjack combat inherited a lot of the familiar Warframe damage types, but with a twist. Impact became Ballistic, Cold became Frost, and so on. We are removing the second layer of ‘Railjack’ Damage types to unify and have the system be based on what Players already spend time learning: core Warframe elements. This means that:
Frost = Cold

patchlogs.name: Warframe Revised: Railjack Revisited (Part 1): Update 27.4
patchlogs.changes:
Our Healing AoE / Damage Reduction changes posted back on April 3rd have arrived! If you’re unfamiliar, ultimately what we want is more ‘Healing’ Abilities to work to allow for more strategies to emerge in various mission types. Healing these objectives can serve well as an alternative or a complement to the commonly used defensive Abilities, such as Frost's Snow Globe, Gara's Mass Vitrify, Limbo's Cataclysm. 100% heals is not what we want to do, so we are instead allowing the effects with some objective-specific adjustments as to not trivialize the game modes.
Banshee, Excalibur Umbra, Frost, Nekros, Nova, Nyx, Saryn, Valkyr, and Zephyr Ability videos have been added to their respective Arsenals!

abilities.description: 發射一道極度低溫的能量來凍結目標。

abilities.description: ระเบิดพลังงานเยือกแข็งที่ทำให้เป้าหมายแข็งตัว

patchlogs.name: Empyrean: Ivara Prime 27.0.11 - 27.0.11.3
patchlogs.changes:
TEMPORARILY removed the Tenebrous Ephemera as a drop from Reinforced Sentient Containers aboard the Sentient Anomaly in Veil Proxima. The drop method is causing numerous issues in terms of connectivity stability and player frustration. We’re going to be changing the acquisition method that won’t involve a direct drop rate in a near future Hotfix/Update, and will instead be closer to a token system (complete X Anomaly missions to buy Ephemera from a vendor).
The Tenebrous Ephemera will be coming back as soon as possible in a better acquisition method

components.name: Blueprint
components.description: Itemize and execute with this pair of auto-lock-on, homing-projectile pistols. Shoot from-hip for a more conventional pistol experience. The patented Granum Attaché System reloads the pistols when holstered.

item.description: Itemize and execute with this pair of auto-lock-on, homing-projectile pistols. Shoot from-hip for a more conventional pistol experience. The patented Granum Attaché System reloads the pistols when holstered.
item.name: Tenet Diplos

patchlogs.name: Update 31.5: Angels of the Zariman
patchlogs.fixes: Fixed the Tenet Diplos’ lock-on ability not damaging Osprey enemies.

patchlogs.name: Update 30.9.0: Prime Resurgence
patchlogs.fixes: Fixed Tenet Diplos lock-on ability not working for the Client players when using a Vehicle (Merulina, K-Drive, etc). As reported here: https://forums.warframe.com/topic/1270984-tenet-diplos-lock-on-not-working-on-k-drive/

patchlogs.name: Nidus Prime & Plague Star: Hotfix 30.7.6
patchlogs.fixes: Fixed the Tenet Diplos reverting to a packed/holstered configuration when trying to customize with skins.

patchlogs.name: Update 30.7: Nidus Prime & Plague Star
patchlogs.fixes: Fixed the Tenet Diplos not unlocking the Meeting Adjourned achievement.

patchlogs.name: Nightwave: Prime Vault: Hotfix 30.6.1
patchlogs.fixes: Fixed mounting and dismounting a K-Drive while using the Tenet Diplos causing its animation to break.

patchlogs.name: Sisters of Parvos: Hotfix 30.5.3
patchlogs.changes: Tenet Diplos clip size increased to 92 and increased ammo pool to 460.

de.name: Tenet Diplos
de.description: Mit diesem Paar zielsuchender Pistolen kann man präzise exekutieren. Schieß aus der Hüfte für ein klassisches Pistolenerlebnis. Das patentierte Granum Attaché-System lädt die Pistolen im Holster nach.

fr.name: Diplos - Principe
fr.description: Mettez vos plans à exécution avec cette paire de pistolets à projectiles à tête chercheuse se verrouillant automatiquement. Les tirs à la hanche permettent une expérience de pistolet plus conventionnelle. Le système breveté 'Attaché Granum' recharge l'arme lorsqu'elle est rangée.

it.name: Tenet Diplos
it.description: Metti in atto i tuoi piani con questa coppia di pistole a proiettile autobloccante. Spara dal fianco per un'esperienza con la pistola più convenzionale. Il sistema brevettato Granum Attaché ricarica le pistole quando riposte nella fondina.

ko.name: 테넷 디플로스
ko.description: 자동 록온 유도 발사체를 발사하는 이 한 쌍의 권총으로 항목을 세분화하고 실행해 보세요. 조준 없이 발사하면 기존의 평범한 권총의 느낌을 만끽하실 수 있습니다. 전매특허의 그라넘 서류함 시스템을 통해 수납 시 자동으로 재장전됩니다.

es.name: Diplos Tenet
es.description: Especifica y ejecuta con este par de pistolas de proyectiles autodirigidos con bloqueo automático. Dispara desde la cadera para una experiencia de pistola más convencional. El sistema patentado Attaché Granum recarga las pistolas cuando están enfundadas.

zh.name: 信条·纵横双枪
zh.description: （英文：TENET DIPLOS）用这对自动锁定追踪目标的双枪将敌人逐个击破。腰射模式与传统手枪无异。配备了获得专利批准的格拉努公文包系统，收起时自动装填。

ru.name: Диплос Догмат
ru.description: Исполняйте свои планы с помощью этого парного оружия, стреляющего самонаводящимися ракетами. Стреляйте от бедра для полноты ощущений. Запатентованная система Грэнума «Дипломат» перезаряжает пистолеты в кобуре.

ja.name: Tenet Diplos
ja.description: オートロックオン技術とホーミング弾を搭載したピストル。ヒップ射撃で従来のピストルの射撃が可能。Granumアタッシュシステムにより収納する事で自動でリロードされる。

pl.name: Diplos Dogmatu
pl.description: Kataloguj i kasuj za pomocą tej pary samonamierzających pistoletów z samonaprowadzającym się pociskiem. Strzelaj z biodra, aby uzyskać bardziej konwencjonalne wrażenia. Opatentowany system Dyplomatki Granuma przeładowuje pistolety w kaburze.

pt.name: Diplos Tenet
pt.description: Esmiúce e execute seus alvos com este par de pistolas com projéteis teleguiados e travamento de mira automático. Atire sem mirar com a arma para ter uma experiência mais convencional. Por meio do patenteado 'Sistema Adido de Granum', a arma é automaticamente recarregada quando guardada no coldre.

tc.name: 教條 敵對
tc.description: （英文：TENET DIPLOS）用這對自動鎖定及發射追蹤型子彈的手槍來將敵人逐一擊斃。腰射模式具有更傳統的手槍體驗。收納時，Granum 公事包系統會重新裝填手槍。

th.name: Tenet Diplos
th.description: ปืนพกที่ยิงกระสุนนำวิถีแบบล็อกเป้าหมายอัตโนมัติคู่นี้จะจดจำรายละเอียดและจัดการศัตรูจนสำเร็จ ยิงได้อย่างรวดเร็วให้ความรู้สึกเหมือนใช้ปืนพกแบบธรรมดา ระบบที่ได้รับการจดสิทธิบัตร Granum Attaché มาแล้วจะบรรจุกระสุนให้ปืนพกใหม่เมื่อใส่ซอง

tr.name: Tenet Diplos
tr.description: Bu hedefe otomatik kilitlenen ve güdümlü mermilere sahip tabanca çifti ile Arsenalini güçlendir. Daha geleneksel bir tabanca deneyimi için nişan almadan ateş et. Patentli Granum Attaché sistemi, tabancalar kılıflandığında onları yeniden doldurur.

uk.name: Дипломат-догмат
uk.description: Парні пістолети, що стріляють самонавідними ракетами. Постріли від стегна додають незабутніх вражень. Запатентована Ґранумом система «Дипломат» перезаряджає зброю, коли вона захована.

de.name: Tenet Arca Plasmor
de.description: Eine angepasste Variante eines Corpus Klassikers. Umwerfende Explosionen prallen jetzt ab und haben eine größere Reichweite, auf Kosten einer geringeren Feuerrate und Nachladegeschwindigkeit. Überlebende Feinde werden von der Strahlung verzehrt.

fr.name: Arca Plasmor - Principe
fr.description: Variante personnalisée d'un classique Corpus. Les tirs déstabilisants ricochent maintenant et ont une plus grande portée au prix d'une cadence de tir et d'une vitesse de rechargement réduites. Les ennemis y survivant seront consumés par les radiations.

it.name: Tenet Arca Plasmor
it.description: Variante personalizzata di un classico Corpus. Le esplosioni ora rimbalzano e hanno una portata maggiore al costo di una velocità di ricarica e fuoco più lente. I nemici sopravvissuti vengono consumati dalle radiazioni.

ko.name: 테넷 아르카 플라즈모어
ko.description: 코퍼스 고전적 무기의 커스텀 변형입니다. 목표물을 비틀거리게 하는 폭발이 표면에서 튕겨 오르며 더 먼 사거리를 갖게 되지만, 낮은 연사력 및 재장전 속도를 가졌습니다. 살아남는 적들은 방사능에 잠식됩니다.

es.name: Plasmor Arca Tenet
es.description: Variante personalizada de un clásico del Corpus. Los estallidos tambaleantes ahora rebotan y tienen mayor alcance a costa de menor velocidad de disparo y de recarga. Los enemigos sobrevivientes son consumidos por la radiación.

zh.name: 信条·弧电离子枪
zh.description: （英文：TENET ARCA PLASMOR）Corpus 经典武器的特制变体。惊人的爆炸会反弹且拥有更高的射程，但代价是更低的射速和装填速度。幸存下来的敌人会被辐射耗尽生命。

ru.name: Арка Плазмор Догмат
ru.description: Модифицированный вариант классики Корпуса. Ошеломляющие выстрелы теперь рикошетят и имеют большую дальность за счёт более медленного огня и скорости перезарядки. Выжившие враги поглощаются ионизирующей радиацией.

ja.name: Tenet Arca Plasmor
ja.description: 従来のコーパス武器のカスタム版。発射速度とリロード速度を犠牲に、発射される射出物は跳ね返り距離が伸びるよう改造された兵器。生き延びた敵には大量の放射線を浴びさせる。

pl.name: Arca Plasmor Dogmatu
pl.description: Niestandardowy wariant klasyka Corpus. Oszałamiające ładunki teraz odbijają się i mają większy zasięg kosztem wolniejszej Szybkostrzelności i Prędkości Przeładowania. Wrogowie, którzy przeżyją, zostają pochłonięci przez radiację.

pt.name: Arca Plasmor Tenet
pt.description: Uma versão personalizada de um equipamento clássico dos Corpus. Explosões atordoantes agora ricocheteiam e possuem maior alcance, ao custo de uma Cadência de Tiro e Velocidade de Recarga mais lenta. Inimigos sobreviventes são consumidos pela radiação.

tc.name: 教條 弧電離子槍
tc.description: （英文：TENET ARCA PLASMOR）Corpus 經典的自訂版本。導致失衡的爆破現在會四處彈射並擁有更大的射程，代價是較低的射速及重新裝填速度。存活下來的敵人將被輻射吞噬。

th.name: Tenet Arca Plasmor
th.description: ปืนกระบอกนี้ดัดแปลงมาจากอาวุธรุ่นคลาสสิกของ Corpus ซึ่งกระสุนที่ยิงออกไปจะกระดอนออกและมีระยะยิงที่ไกลกว่า แต่ก็ต้องแลกกลับการยิงและการรีโหลดกระสุนที่ช้าลง ศัตรูที่รอดตายจะถูกแผดเผาด้วยรังสี

tr.name: Tenet Arca Plasmor
tr.description: Bir Corpus Klasiğinin özel varyantı. Dengeyi bozan atışlar artık sekiyor. Atış hızı ile yeniden yükleme hızı azaltıldı fakat artık daha fazla menzile sahip. Hayatta kalan düşmanlar radyasyon tarafından tüketilir.

uk.name: Арка-Плазмор-догмат
uk.description: Оновлений варіант класичної рушниці Корпусу. Оглушливі постріли тепер рикошетять і мають більшу дальність дії. Швидкість стрільби й заряджання зменшена. Якщо хто вціліє, то страждає від опромінення.

ja.name: Protovyre エフェメラ

pl.name: Efemera: Protovyre

tc.name: 原幻血變幻紋

th.name: อิเฟมเมอรา Protovyre

tr.name: Protovyre Ephemera
